# parse-ms-2

> This can parse milliseconds into an object

## Install

```
$ npm install parse-ms-2
```

## Usage

```js
require('parse-ms-2')

parseMilliseconds(1337000001)


/*
Return:

{
	days: 15,
	hours: 11,
	minutes: 23,
	seconds: 20,
	milliseconds: 1,
	microseconds: 0,
	nanoseconds: 0
}
*/
```
